{
  "title": "Romantic Syrian Long Bean Pilaf",
  "description": "A funky and silky Syrian dish featuring long beans, this pilaf is a romantic and egg-free friendly option for any meal. It combines the flavors of the Middle East with the simplicity of a one-pot dish.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
